### Call to action
The call to action button should be used when a link to a new page is the primary call to action on a page. For example, a “Start survey” link.

Links simply styled as buttons are not accessible to users who navigate a web page with voice commands. Setting `"url"` will add the attribute `role="button"` which will help these users select the link.
