}}

### Ghost
The ghosted button style is for use in the [header](/components/header/#external-with-language-and-save-button) or [footer](/components/footer). This can be used to allow a user to exit or [save and sign out](/patterns/save-and-sign-out) of a service.

Setting `"variants"` with `'ghost'` will style the button, and setting `iconType` with `exit` adds the appropriate icon for a “sign out” or “exit” button.
